query:
SELECT 
            name,
            game_system,
            rarity,
            level,
            price,
            GROUP_CONCAT(tag) AS tags
        FROM library_objects lo
        INNER JOIN library_items li ON lo.id = li.id
        INNER JOIN library_objects_tags lot ON lo.id = lot.library_object_id
        INNER JOIN tags t ON lot.tag_id = t.id
        GROUP BY lo.id
